1.4.0
=====

2019-11-07

* New packaging.
* Add README and manual page.
* Upgrade dependency on yad-lib.sh 1.2.0.
* Remove dependency on netpbm-advanced.
* Fully integrated list item right-click editing (add, change, delete).
* Add Properties button in Help window.
* New Copy button.
* Aggregate Edit, Clear, Copy buttons under the new Copy button.
* Allow items to contain "|" (set new variable DNDMATE_SEPARATOR).
* New options: --tail, --uncheck-drop, --uncheck-append, --info, --icon-get, --clean, --append-exit.
* Extend option --exit to --exit[=CODE].
* Remove option --no-restart.
* Allow indenting --optf FILE.
* Much improved and updated runtime help page.
* New /usr/shared/command-samples.en.txt.
* New styles in /usr/share/dndmate/stylef.
* New presets random-no-id.opt, random-lowercase-id.opt and random-uppercase-id.opt in /usr/local/apps/dndmate/res/.
* Ensure ASCII for icon path.
* Fix anybody can read user's temporary files.
* Fix window icon keeps changing when a randomly-chosen style is involved.
* Fix resized window keeps going back to compact style.
* Fix two long-forgotten issues.
* Fix null characters in DNDMATE_REFS.
* Fix out-of-order multi-dropped items.
* Fix bash 4.4 portability issue.
* Fix parsing command line when there are no options.
* Performance and documentation improvements; other bugs fixed.
* ROX-app: add more icons (R, G, B, Bl, W).
* ROX-app: menu left-click implies --optf=res/default.opt, which sets compact window style.

1.3.0
=====

2018-08-04

* Require yad >= 0.40.3 commit b3a99043 2018-06-07.
* New: instance windows maintain their position and size (require yad-lib).
* New options: --stylef, --width, --height, --fgcolor, --bgcolor, --font-family, --opt, --glyph-scale.
* New: default style file prepared for Djavu Sans font.
* New: matching application icon and drop target glyph.
* New: random application icons.
* New: application icon and drop target foreground and background color support.
* New: Autofit drop target glyph for horizontal layout.
* New: Initial window width is unconstrained (was 300 px).
* Changed: removed feature: DNDMATE_DANGER_RE; renamed some command-line options.
* Updated: Help/usage text.
* Fixed: --close didn't work correctly. Many other fixes.
* ROX-app: add menu entry to start dndmate with a random icon.

1.2.0
=====

2017-08-11

* Now option --id without =ID auto-generates ID.
* New option --optfile=FILE to read options from FILE.
* New option --symbol to change drop target background graphics.
* Add various media symbols based on font DejaVu Sans.
* New option --uniq.
* New usage warning for "--close -a refs".
* Improve help.
* ROX-app: change menu entries.
* ROX-app: add --id=media entry.

1.1.0
=====

2017-03-16

* First public release

